name: Ford Motor
description: Ford Motor Company is an automobile company. The Company designs, manufactures, markets, and services a full line of electrified passenger and commercial vehicles, such as Ford trucks, utility vehicles, vans, and cars, and Lincoln luxury vehicles.

name: Lamborghini
description: Automobili Lamborghini S.p.A. (Italian pronunciation: is an Italian brand and manufacturer of luxury sports cars and SUVs based in Sant'Agata Bolognese. The company is owned by the Volkswagen Group through its subsidiary Audi.

name: Tesla
description: Tesla was founded in 2003 by a group of engineers who wanted to compromise to drive vehicles can be better, quicker and more fun to drive than gasoline cars. Today, Tesla builds not only all-electric vehicles but also infinitely scalable clean energy generation and storage products.
